### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CSharpEssentials.LoggerHelper Demo — 1-Click API Test Suite
### Run with:  dotnet run --project src/CSharpEssentials.LoggerHelper.Demo
### Then fire each request to exercise every endpoint.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ── Basic Logging ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Simple Information log
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basic/info

### 2. All 6 log levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basic/levels

### 3. Structured properties (OrderId, Customer, Amount)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basic/structured

### 4. Exception logged at Error level
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basic/exception

### ── Trace API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5. BeginTrace scope — multi-step operation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trace/scope

### 6. Single-shot trace with exception
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trace/single-shot

### 7. Shorthand trace (Information, no exception)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trace/shorthand

### ── Custom Properties ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 8. Custom scope properties (CustomerId, Region, TenantId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/scope

### 9. Nested scopes (BeginTrace + custom)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/nested

### 10. Inline structured properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/properties/inline

### ── Routing Demo ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### 11. Fire all levels — verify per-sink routing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/routing/test

### 12. Show internal errors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/routing/errors

### 13. Show active configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/routing/config

### ── Diagnostics ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### 14. Pipeline health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diagnostics/health

### 15. Clear internal error store
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/diagnostics/errors

### ── Dynamic File Routing ──────────────────────────────────────

### 16. Single tenant logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/file-dynamic/tenant/acme

### 17. Multi-tenant logs (3 tenants)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/file-dynamic/multi-tenant

### 18. No tenant (base path fallback)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/file-dynamic/no-tenant

### 19. Mixed tenant / no-tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/file-dynamic/mixed

### 20. Verify log files on disk
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/file-dynamic/verify

### ── Sensitive Data Masking ────────────────────────────────────

### 21. Mask email, password, credit card
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/masking/login

### 22. Mask Bearer token, connection string, custom regex
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/masking/api-error

### ── MCP Server ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 23. List available MCP tools
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp-demo/tools

### 24. Call MCP tool — health
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp-demo/call/get-health

### 25. Call MCP tool — errors
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp-demo/call/get-errors

### 26. Call MCP tool — sinks
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp-demo/call/get-sinks

### 27. Call MCP tool — config
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mcp-demo/call/get-config

### 28. Raw MCP JSON-RPC — list tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"method":"tools/list","params":{}}

### 29. Raw MCP JSON-RPC — get health
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":2,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_get_health","arguments":{}}}

### ── Sampling (v5.2.0) ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 30. Emit 100 logs — observe sampling per sink
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sampling/burst

### 31. Show sampling config for all routes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sampling/config

### ── Dashboard (v5.3.0) ────────────────────────────────────────

### 32. Open embedded diagnostics dashboard (HTML page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/loggerhelper-dashboard

### 33. Dashboard JSON API — raw diagnostics data
GET {{baseUrl}}/loggerhelper-dashboard/api/data
